Arian Foster , Texans running back Why he matters: Sure, Matt Schaub is capable of throwing for a lot of yards, but the Texans' success for the near term hangs on defense and ball control, and nobody controls the ball better than the Foster - Earl Campbell incarnate in terms of substance, if not style - we've seen the last two seasons.
